org.sakaiproject.sms.hibernate.model
Class SmsTransaction

java.lang.Object
  org.sakaiproject.sms.hibernate.model.BaseModel
      org.sakaiproject.sms.hibernate.model.SmsTransaction
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class SmsTransaction
extends BaseModel

Transactions linked to a specific sms account. When a sms task is created, a transaction will be inserted indicating that credits are reserved. When the task is processed, the actual credits will be calculated and the difference will be settled with another transaction.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Julian Wyngaard
